      🌐 Translation Add/Update: Chinese (Simplified)

      Based on #524 Deleted the wrong spelling branch and re-PR with co-author and correct branch name
      基于 #524 删除了错误的拼写分支，并与合著者一起使用正确的分支名重新提交了 PR
      Based on #517, which already provided a solid foundation for the Chinese localization,
      基于 #517 ，它已经为中文本地化提供了坚实的基础，
      This pull request completes the remaining untranslated parts(The original translator XMxmx111 has translated some of the content perfectly) — specifically images, loading animations, and other UI-related content.
      这个 pull request 完成了剩余的未翻译部分（原始翻译者 XMxmx111 已经完美地翻译了一些内容）—— 具体是图片、加载动画和其他与 UI 相关的内容。

      Specifically:  具体来说：

      • ✅ Translated INI documentation entries into Mandarin - Simplified Chinese.
        ✅ 已将 INI 文档条目翻译成简体中文。
      • 🖼️ Added translations for UI images where applicable (e.g., loading screens, interface elements,launcherupdater,legaltext etc...).
        🖼️ 已为适用的 UI 图像添加翻译（例如，加载屏幕、界面元素、launcherupdater、legaltext 等）。
      • 🔄 Included translations for loading animations and related text prompts.
        🔄 已包含加载动画及相关文本提示的翻译。

      All translations aim to preserve consistency with existing language style and follow the original context accurately.Meanwhile Chinese-Traditional(zh-hant) is on the way.
      所有翻译均旨在保持与现有语言风格的连贯性，并准确遵循原始语境。同时，简体中文(zh-hans)正在推进中。
      Please review and let us know if any adjustments are needed. TQVM
      请审阅，如有任何需要调整的地方，请告知。谢谢。
